entry.string: The same registered ID (#(1)) was found belonging to a #(2) theme in the file system and a registered #(3) theme in the database. Please correct this and regenerate the list.
entry.translation: Zee seme-a regeestered ID (#(1)) ves fuoond belungeeng tu a #(2) zeeme-a in zee feele-a system und a regeestered #(3) zeeme-a in zee detebese-a. Pleese-a currect thees und regenerete-a zee leest. Um de hur de hur de hur.
